Welcome to the official public repository for iLoveLaTeX project submissions.

This repository is dedicated to collecting, tracking, and managing example projects, templates, test files, and community contributions related to the iLoveLaTeX platform.

ğŸ¯ Purpose of This Repository

The main goals of this repository are:

Provide sample input files (PDF, DOCX, LaTeX) used for testing conversions

Share public LaTeX templates and publisher-specific structures

Collect bug reproduction cases to improve conversion accuracy

Enable community contributions for templates, layouts, and improvements

Ensure transparency and reproducibility of conversion results

