ğŸ Minimal files that reproduce a specific issue or bug

ğŸ“š Academic or publisher-oriented template examples

âš ï¸ Important:
Please make sure that all submitted files are free of personal, confidential, or copyrighted content, unless you have the explicit right to share them publicly.

ğŸ§¾ Submission Guidelines

To submit a project:

Fork this repository

Create a new folder under the appropriate category

Add a short README.md describing:

The purpose of the submission

Input format and expected output

Any known issues or constraints

Open a Pull Request with a clear and concise description

ğŸ¤ Contribution Policy

All contributions are welcome and appreciated.
By submitting content to this repository, you agree that your contribution may be used to:

Improve conversion quality

Train and evaluate document processing pipelines

Enhance template compatibility and coverage

ğŸŒ About iLoveLaTeX

iLoveLaTeX is a platform designed to simplify and automate the conversion of documents into high-quality LaTeX, with a strong focus on academic publishing, scientific templates, and publisher compliance.

